Image to Text Converter :
A simple web application that extracts text from images using OCR (Optical Character Recognition) with Tesseract.js

Features :

Upload any image (PNG, JPG, JPEG).
Preview the selected image before conversion.
Extract text directly from the image.
Clean and responsive user interface.

How It Works :

Upload an image using the file input.
The app displays a preview of the image.
Click Convert Image to Text to extract the text.
The extracted text appears in the textarea below.

Technologies Used :

HTML5 & CSS3 – Structure and styling.
JavaScript – Logic for file handling and OCR.
Tesseract.js – OCR engine for extracting text from images.

Usage :

Clone or download the repository.
Open awt2.html in your browser.
Upload an image and click the convert button.
